LOSING ITS IDENTITY. DURING THE SMALL HOURS OF WEDNESDAY A SECOND LOW 972
SPREADS INTO THE FAR W FM THE ATLANTIC. THIS GRADUALLY MOVS EWARDS FLN SLTLY
